org.fujion.test

Class MockEnvironment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.test.MockEnvironment

  • public class MockEnvironment
extends Object
    This class creates a mock Fujion environment suitable for certain kinds of unit tests. It creates a web app instance with a single page, a mock session and execution context and a single application context.
